spec_data.Name: mingw32-dlfcn
spec_data.Description:
This library implements a wrapper for dlfcn, as specified in POSIX and SUS,
around the dynamic link library functions found in the Windows API.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 08:48:44 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Implements a wrapper for dlfcn (dlopen dlclose dlsym dlerror)
